About Moula

[/vc_column][vc_column width=”1/3″ css=”.vc_custom_1525350218399{margin-bottom: 0px !important;}”]
Boilerplate
[vc_column_text el_class=”lead”]Since 2013, Moula has been creating the future of business finance. With our Intelligent Decisioning Engine, Moula is changing how business experiences financial services.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=”2/3″]
Short description
[vc_column_text]Moula is an Australian fintech empowering good businesses with funding to help them grow.

We’re democratising access to smart business finance. Integrating a business’ cloud accounting and banking data, we use artificial intelligence and machine learning to deliver decisions within 24 hours. We take a ‘heads and hearts’ approach to improve every customer’s experience, which means balancing the data, automation and tech, with the personal, human touch.

Over the years, tens of thousands of businesses have benefitted from Moula, accessing more than half a billion dollars in growth capital. [/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=”stretch_row_content” content_placement=”middle” equal_height=”yes” remove_bottom_col_margin=”true” visibility=”hidden”][vc_column typography_style=”white” css=”.vc_custom_1567487878173{padding-top: 3rem !important;padding-bottom: 3rem !important;background-color: #0ac6a6 !important;}” el_class=”text-center” offset=”vc_col-md-6″ min_height=”400px”]
